## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="f49b0-102">輸入的模式<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>取決於其<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f49b0-102">The input mode for an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> is determined by its <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f49b0-103">預設值輸入的模式是指出所定義之文法的語音<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>會比對的語音輸入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f49b0-103">The default input mode is Voice, which indicates that the grammar defined by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument> will match speech input.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f49b0-104">Dtmf 模式表示文法會比對雙重撥號音後開始多頻率 (DTMF) 色調，而不是語音。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f49b0-104">The Dtmf mode indicates that a grammar will match Dual-Tone Multi-Frequency (DTMF) tones instead of speech.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="f49b0-105">有 16 DTMF 撥號音，其中 12 常見大部分的電話。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f49b0-105">There are 16 DTMF tones, 12 of which are commonly found on most telephones.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="f49b0-106">當您建立<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>物件從<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>物件會比對所指定的輸入類型<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A>屬性，取得的執行個體<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="f49b0-106">When you create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object from an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument>, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> object will match the type of input specified by the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsDocument.Mode%2A> property, which gets an instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsGrammarMode>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
string srgsDocumentFile = Path.Combine(Path.GetTempPath(), "srgsDocumentFile.xml");  
SrgsDocument document = null;  
GrammarBuilder builder = null;  
Grammar grammar = null;  
  
Choices firstThree = new Choices(new string[] {"1", "2", "3"});  
Choices nextThree = new Choices(new string[] {"4", "5", "6"});  
Choices lastThree = new Choices(new string[] {"7", "8", "9"});  
  
Choices keyPadChoices = new Choices(new GrammarBuilder[] {firstThree, nextThree, lastThree, new Choices("0")});  
  
builder = new GrammarBuilder(keyPadChoices);  
document = new SrgsDocument(builder);  
  
document.Mode = SrgsGrammarMode.Dtmf;  
grammar = new Grammar(document);   
```
